OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1781100698
OL,3,CMan sentenced under new sex
OL,4,Charrassment law after grabbing woman's
OL,5,Chair on train
OL,7,FWatch: David Stroud is questioned by
OL,8,Fjournalists after being sentenced for
OL,9,Fharrassment, apologising to his victim
OL,10,Fand blaming alcohol for his behaviour
OL,12,FA man from Kent who repeatedly grabbed
OL,13,Fa young woman's hair and asked to kiss
OL,14,Fher on a train has been sentenced to a
OL,15,F12-month community order in a landmark
OL,16,Fcase.
OL,18,FDavid Stroud made several unwanted
OL,19,Fsexual comments to the other passenger
OL,20,Fduring a journey from Hastings to
OL,21,FLondon.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1781100698
OL,3,CMan sentenced under new sex
OL,4,Charrassment law after grabbing woman's
OL,5,Chair on train
OL,7,FIt happened on 3 April, two days after
OL,8,Fa new law came into force banning
OL,9,Fharassment because of a person's sex.
OL,11,FThe 44-year-old father-of-two had
OL,12,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to a
OL,13,Fseparate 22-month stalking campaign,
OL,14,Fthe court heard on Tuesday.
OL,16,FHe had been on bail for stalking when
OL,17,Fhe harassed the victim on the train.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1781100698
OL,3,CMan sentenced under new sex
OL,4,Charrassment law after grabbing woman's
OL,5,Chair on train
OL,7,FStroud from Dartford tried to make
OL,8,Fconversation with the woman, who
OL,9,Fattempted to ignore him as she was a
OL,10,Flone female travelling, the court
OL,11,Fheard.
OL,13,FThe woman said she could smell alcohol
OL,14,Fon the defendant's breath.
OL,16,FStroud, a father-of-two, told the
OL,17,Fwoman "you're never going to find
OL,18,Fsomeone who loves your hair as much as
OL,19,FI do", and she replied, "I already
OL,20,Fhave someone".
OL,26,@yD@GOU{D@EO]{D@YOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1781100698
OL,3,CMan sentenced under new sex
OL,4,Charrassment law after grabbing woman's
OL,5,Chair on train
OL,7,FThe woman's boyfriend heard the
OL,8,Fcomments over the phone and called the
OL,9,FBritish Transport Police, who arrested
OL,10,FStroud at London Bridge station.
OL,12,FWhile under caution Stroud said: "It's
OL,13,Fjust banter, we had banter together,
OL,14,Fdo you know what I mean?" the court
OL,15,Fheard.
OL,17,FHe also said: "I've done nothing wrong
OL,18,Fto her."
OL,26,@tD@bOUvD@YO]yD@OOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1781100698
OL,3,CMan sentenced under new sex
OL,4,Charrassment law after grabbing woman's
OL,5,Chair on train
OL,7,FThe new offence, under Section 4B of
OL,8,Fthe Public Order Act 1986, covers
OL,9,Fintentional harassment directed at
OL,10,Fsomeone because of their sex,
OL,11,Fincluding where perpetrators target
OL,12,Fwomen and girls in public places,
OL,13,Fincluding streets, parks and public
OL,14,Ftransport.
OL,16,FStroud was sentenced for both offences
OL,17,Fand was spared jail, receiving a 12-
OL,18,Fmonth community order and being told
OL,19,Fto complete 15 days of rehabilitation
OL,20,Factivity requirement.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1781100698
OL,3,CMan sentenced under new sex
OL,4,Charrassment law after grabbing woman's
OL,5,Chair on train
OL,7,FHe has also been ordered to carry out
OL,8,F150 hours' unpaid work and be fitted
OL,9,Fwith an alcohol abstinence monitoring
OL,10,Ftag for 90 days.
OL,12,FDistrict Judge Caroline Jackson also
OL,13,Fmade a five-year restraining order
OL,14,Fagainst him for the stalking victim.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1781100698
OL,3,CMan sentenced under new sex
OL,4,Charrassment law after grabbing woman's
OL,5,Chair on train
OL,7,FOlivia Rose, deputy chief Crown
OL,8,Fprosecutor and the Crown Prosecution
OL,9,FService's (CPS) lead on stalking, said
OL,10,Fshe hopes the law and Stroud's
OL,11,Fprosecution send a message to would-be
OL,12,Foffenders: "If you think you are going
OL,13,Fto get away with sex-based harassment
OL,14,Fbecause you consider it just to be
OL,15,Ffriendly banter, it isn't.
OL,17,F"This is a serious offence and you
OL,18,Fwill be prosecuted."
OL,26,@tD@LOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
