PN,41708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1781100698
OL,3,CMan sentenced under new sex
OL,4,Charrassment law after grabbing woman's
OL,5,Chair on train
OL,7,FIn a written statement, Stroud's
OL,8,Fvictim said she struggles to get on
OL,9,Fpublic transport and is always on
OL,10,Fconstant alert.
OL,12,FShe said: "David Stroud's crime has
OL,13,Fimpacted every part of my life. I now
OL,14,Fstruggle to get on public transport,
OL,15,Fespecially trains, both alone and with
OL,16,Ffriends. When I do travel, I'm on
OL,17,Fconstant alert and I'm extra vigilant.
OL,18,FIt's also impacted my boyfriend who is
OL,19,Fworried about me every time I leave
OL,20,Fthe house.
OL,26,@tD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1781100698
OL,3,CMan sentenced under new sex
OL,4,Charrassment law after grabbing woman's
OL,5,Chair on train
OL,7,F"This isn't the first time I've
OL,8,Fexperienced a sexual offence so his
OL,9,Factions resurfaced a lot of bad
OL,10,Fmemories for me. And since it happened
OL,11,FI've suffered from panic attacks and
OL,12,Fnight terrors. Women are used to this
OL,13,Fhappening to them, whereas men are not.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1781100698
OL,3,CMan sentenced under new sex
OL,4,Charrassment law after grabbing woman's
OL,5,Chair on train
OL,7,F"Some men may see this case and
OL,8,Fdismiss David Stroud's actions as
OL,9,Fbanter or just someone being drunk.
OL,10,FBut they don't have the same fears as
OL,11,Fwomen. We have to think about what
OL,12,Fstreets we walk down and have to be
OL,13,Fconstantly aware of the dangers of
OL,14,Fassault or harassment at the hands of
OL,15,Fmen.
OL,17,F"Everything women have to think about,
OL,18,Fmen just don't have to consider.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1781100698
OL,3,CMan sentenced under new sex
OL,4,Charrassment law after grabbing woman's
OL,5,Chair on train
OL,7,F"On the train I was cornered by
OL,8,Fsomeone four times the size of me
OL,9,Fwhich is a really intimidating
OL,10,Fsituation to be in. I've been really
OL,11,Fsurprised by the response from British
OL,12,FTransport Police. They came straight
OL,13,Faway and arrested David Stroud on the
OL,14,Fplatform and it was taken really
OL,15,Fseriously from the outset.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1781100698
OL,3,CMan sentenced under new sex
OL,4,Charrassment law after grabbing woman's
OL,5,Chair on train
OL,7,F"They have also kept me informed
OL,8,Fthroughout. This justice proves it's
OL,9,Fworth reporting to police as it will
OL,10,Fbe taken seriously, as it was in my
OL,11,Fcase. Nothing is going to change if
OL,12,Fthese crimes are not reported and go
OL,13,Funpunished.
OL,15,F"It's 2026 ` we need to move forward
OL,16,Fand look at these things seriously so
OL,17,Fpeople like David Stroud stop getting
OL,18,Faway with it."
OL,26,@zD@NO]
